fulltitle: Gonzalo Rubalcaba | Home Life with Gonzalo
title: Gonzalo Rubalcaba | Home Life with Gonzalo
description: Gonzalo Rubalcaba, one of the world's premiere pianist, describes his Life in Cuba and how his background shaped his musical dreams. This interview was graciously conducted in his home in South Florida while discussing the power of one his favorite software tools, Pianoteq.
